Name: Cabela's Big Game Hunter: Hunting Party

Achievements.Name: Prepare to Hunt!
Achievements.Description: Play the game for the first time.

Achievements.Name: The Texan Survivor
Achievements.Description: Brave the Texas wilderness and all it has to offer in Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: The Mexican Heat
Achievements.Description: Brave the Mexican wilderness and all it has to offer in Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: The Canadian Tracker
Achievements.Description: Brave the wilds of British Columbia and all it has to offer in Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: The Safari Master
Achievements.Description: Brave the Tanzanian wilderness and all it has to offer in Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: Survived the Fantasy Reserve
Achievements.Description: Complete Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: Perkified
Achievements.Description: Acquire the maximum level for all perks in Story Mode.

Achievements.Name: Glass Jaw
Achievements.Description: Perform a stunning shot to a game animal's head. Attainable in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Clean Shot
Achievements.Description: Bag animal by hitting it's vitals and bringing it down in one shot. Attainable in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Ruined Trophies
Achievements.Description: Continue to perform stunning shots to game animals heads.

Achievements.Name: Im All Win!
Achievements.Description: Master the Clean Shot in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Clustered!
Achievements.Description: Bag 5 birds in one shot. Attainable in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Now Thats Skill!
Achievements.Description: Bag 10 animals in a row with 6x multiplier.

Achievements.Name: Scoped In
Achievements.Description: Bag 30 legal animals while zoomed in with your scope.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Trophy
Achievements.Description: Bag your first Legendary Trophy.

Achievements.Name: Bird Watcher
Achievements.Description: Bag 100 birds in any region. Totals can be accumulated in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Bird Connoisseur
Achievements.Description: Bag 1,000 birds throughout all game modes.

Achievements.Name: Crate Crasher!
Achievements.Description: Bust open twenty crates.

Achievements.Name: POWER-UP!
Achievements.Description: Activate your first power-up in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Slooowww Dowwwn...
Achievements.Description: Activate 25 Slow Motion power-ups.

Achievements.Name: Long Jumper
Achievements.Description: Successfully jump 10 obstacles in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Watch Your Head!
Achievements.Description: Successfully duck 10 obstacles in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Bear Kicker!
Achievements.Description: Have some guts...Kick a bear!

Achievements.Name: Sneaky Sneaky
Achievements.Description: Successfully prove your stealth abilities 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Take Cover!
Achievements.Description: Successfully get behind cover 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Advantage Hunter
Achievements.Description: Activate power-ups 10 times during gameplay.

Achievements.Name: A Solid Defense
Achievements.Description: Perform 15 successful kicks on predators.  Bears dont count.

Achievements.Name: Hand Off
Achievements.Description: Start a Versus match.

Achievements.Name: King of the Hill
Achievements.Description: Win a Versus match against one or more players.

Achievements.Name: Survival Instincts
Achievements.Description: Last for 8 minutes in any gallery Survival level.

Achievements.Name: Sharpshooter
Achievements.Description: Finish a hunt with 100% accuracy.

Achievements.Name: Savior of the Herd
Achievements.Description: Finish a level without bagging an animal illegally. (Fifteen shot minimum required on level.)

Achievements.Name: No Monkey Business!
Achievements.Description: Bag the only two baboons in Iringa.
